    "name": "White Sand Boutique Hotel",
    "detail": "First time in Da Nang for me and my partner and we did not know what to expect. We chose White Sand Hotel due to its 4-star status and affordable rates. The room we had is nothing out of the extraordinary and you can expect all the basics (cleanliness, mini bar, Cable TV) but what made our whole trip even more great were the staff. We were greeted everyday from the point of check-in to check-out with things like “how is everything, where do you plan to go today?” just so they could check on how we were doing. The staff compromising of young people are all exceptionally bright and genuine and they try their absolute best to hold a conversation in English with us. A special shoutout to Fairy, Pooh, Kie, Tony, Peter, Zin, the bellboy and security uncle for making our trip even more memorable. Do give this hotel a go if you’re looking for good location, clean rooms but more importantly, homely service. :)",
